data.description: Come see this beautiful 3 bedroom/ 2 bath single family pool home in the suburban city of Altamonte Springs.  This home is equipped with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and ceramic tile flooring.  Step outside to the spacious backyard, perfect for outdoor gatherings and enjoying the Florida sunshine.  The roof was replaced in February of 2023 and the driveway was paved in August of 2023.   Conveniently located near shopping, dining, and its about thirty minutes from Disney, Universal Studios, and the Orlando International Airport.  Don't miss your chance to make this your new home. Contact us today to schedule a viewing!
